org.anyframe.scheduling.impl
Class SchedulingServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.anyframe.scheduling.impl.SchedulingServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SchedulingService, Aware, ApplicationContextAware
public class SchedulingServiceImpl
extends Object
implements SchedulingService, ApplicationContextAware

This service enable quartz jobs to manage jobs with quartz API.

SchedulingService Configuration Example: 

 <property name="scheduler" ref="schedulerFactoryBean" />
 <property name="jobResultCollector" ref="schedulingJobListener" />
 <property name="scheduler" value="database" />
 <property name="jobResultPath" value="/Anyframe/schedule/" />

Author:
Sujeong Lee
